_Nif’al_ Future Tense:
The _nif’al_ has an [[future tense]] which is one of the [[Nif’al Forms|forms of the nif’al binyan]].
- The _nif’al_ future tense has [[_nif’al_ Future Tense for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _nif’al_ future tense has conjugations for irregular shorushim which will be added at a later time.
